text: Frankenstein Created Woman is a 1967 British Hammer horror movie. It was directed by Terence Fisher. It is the fourth movie in the Hammer's Frankenstein series. Actors include Peter Cushing, Susan Denberg, Derek Fowlds, Barry Warden, Thorley Walters, Robert Morris, and Colin Jeavons.
